Rule 3 ‚Äî All Spells Must Be Reversible

Praus + Aion provide ‚Äúreset to calm ground.‚Äù

Rule 4 ‚Äî Mirror Has Absolute Authority

Mirror can block, rewrite, throttle, or nullify any spell.

Rule 5 ‚Äî Shadow Archetype Is Symbolic Only

13th Coil operates strictly in detection, not actuation.

